---
import { AWAKEN_URL } from '../consts';
const ctaHref = AWAKEN_URL;
---

<section class="relative py-20 lg:py-36 bg-ink text-plaster overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-[0.04]" style="background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(245,240,230,1) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 20% 100%;"></div>

  <div class="absolute -top-24 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[300px] h-[300px] sm:w-[600px] sm:h-[600px] rounded-full bg-brand/8 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute -bottom-32 right-10 w-24 h-24 arabesque-divider opacity-20 hidden lg:block"></div>

  <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 text-center">
    <p class="reveal eyebrow mb-5" style="color:white;">The next step is small. The shift is not.</p>

    <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1 font-display text-[28px] xs:text-[34px] sm:text-5xl lg:text-[76px] leading-[1.1] sm:leading-[1.05] lg:leading-[0.98] text-plaster text-balance">
      Stop drifting.<br />
      <span class="text-brand-soft">Start building with direction.</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2 mt-6 sm:mt-8 text-base sm:text-lg lg:text-xl text-plaster/90 leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto text-pretty">
      Awaken is the first movement of the Young & Aligned Framework. A structured way to understand yourself, think clearly, and move with intention.
    </p>

    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 mt-10 sm:mt-12 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a href={ctaHref} class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-6 sm:px-8 py-3 sm:py-4 rounded-full bg-plaster text-ink hover:bg-brand hover:text-ink transition-all duration-500 text-sm sm:text-base font-medium tracking-wide">
        <span>Join Awaken</span>
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" class="transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:translate-x-1.5"><path d="M1 7h12m0 0L7 1m6 6L7 13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>